What is the length of the midsegment, IJ, of triangle FGH?

x..................
IJ = GH / 2
3x = (2x + 4) / 2
3x = x + 2
2x = 2
x = 1

IJ.................
IJ = 3x
IJ = 3(1)
IJ = 3

