What is the length of side AB?
AB is parallel to DE.

x......................
DE = AB / 2
x + 11 = 9(x - 3) / 2
2x + 22 = 9(x - 3)
2x + 22 = 9x - 27
2x + 49 = 9x
49 = 7x
7 = x

AB.....................
AB = 9(x - 3)
AB = 9(7 - 3)
AB = 9(4)
AB = 36

