What is the length of side WY?
AB is parallel to WY.

x.....................
AB = WY / 2
x + 3 = (3x - 5) / 2
2x + 6 = 3x - 5
2x + 11 = 3x
11 = x

WY....................
WY = 3x - 5
WY = 3(11) - 5
WY = 33 - 5
WY = 28

