Segment XY is a midsegment of triangle ABC. What is the length of segment XY?

x.....................
XY = AG / 2
x + 3 = (4x + 1) / 2
2x + 6 = 4x + 1
6 = 2x + 1
5 = 2x
2.5 = x

XY....................
XY = x + 3
XY = 2.5 + 3
XY = 5.5

